{"id": 2593, "genre": 1001, "title": "除了年龄，你还有哪些独特的“人生进制”？", "description": "如果不把时间当作计算单位的话，你还会从哪些事件的累积中获得“成长感”？（题图来自：iStock ©️CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 3282, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201810292350448rBdWqV5pHhZosmO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-09T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 309760, "content": "看看老爹的人生，感觉自己根本没什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1488769}, {"id": 309761, "content": "一份全新的工作。\n现在在读书", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 310017, "content": "练好一个比较秀的英雄", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498637}, {"id": 309762, "content": "一群完全没接触过的人群\n成了朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 310018, "content": "每次感动后的收获", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498661}, {"id": 309763, "content": "买不起想要的东西的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349158}, {"id": 310275, "content": "软件每崩一次，人就脱一层皮。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1426274}, {"id": 309764, "content": "发现“成长”是不存在的，存在的只有“成长感”", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1251294}, {"id": 309766, "content": "每打完一次手枪都感觉身体越来越虚弱", "image": null, "praise_count": 218, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497792}, {"id": 310022, "content": "忽略时间的流水写作，去除记日历的时间模式，成长暗藏其中", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1495478}, {"id": 310534, "content": "每天的晨跑 从满天繁星到旭日东升 突然想起刺客信条：我们躬身于黑暗 侍奉于光明", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499561}, {"id": 309767, "content": "家人离世", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212802}, {"id": 310024, "content": "经理孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498737}, {"id": 310536, "content": "钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499272}, {"id": 309769, "content": "又学了一门新技能", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479288}, {"id": 310025, "content": "工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498739}, {"id": 309770, "content": "  每次还卡前，都觉得自己还有点钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462811}, {"id": 310026, "content": "每失去一个重要的人，都会想清很多事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403747}, {"id": 310282, "content": "工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500286}, {"id": 309771, "content": "失败", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496987}, {"id": 310539, "content": "听冷门的歌，看冷门的电影，读冷门的书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1126643}, {"id": 309772, "content": "见识，见识不同的世界，吸收不同的世界观", "image": "img/option/option/20181109122323pB20tFYRSMOcUsdD.jpg", "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1495404}, {"id": 310028, "content": "看书单算吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974576}, {"id": 310284, "content": "一次重要的挫折", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500516}, {"id": 309773, "content": "但愿我死的时候身上都是伤疤–Taylor·Durden", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665111}, {"id": 310029, "content": "越长大越有罪恶感", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493632}, {"id": 309774, "content": "进入到新阶段，比如高中进大学，大学进社会", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377387}, {"id": 310030, "content": "每次看完很有启发的电影之后。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482260}, {"id": 310031, "content": "搬了几次家", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1430930}, {"id": 309776, "content": "年龄根本不算人生进制。😞", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451499}, {"id": 310032, "content": "每次新的艳遇", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833845}, {"id": 309777, "content": "小孩越长越大，皱纹越来越多，身体越来越累，心智越来越成熟，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1481542}, {"id": 310545, "content": "很好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418072}, {"id": 309778, "content": "学习，读书，工作，没有一个是一样的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496887}, {"id": 310034, "content": "每次回顾曾经经历的事情，或者细细咀嚼自己和别人曾做过的选择，再或者完成一个阶段的学习、工作、阅读。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911878}, {"id": 309779, "content": "与一些看似不起眼的人聊天，发现背后确实不凡的经历", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497802}, {"id": 310035, "content": "每和一个人闹崩一次都多了解了别人一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475763}, {"id": 309780, "content": "喜欢一个新的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424243}, {"id": 310036, "content": "每次犯错后", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498839}, {"id": 309781, "content": "孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497804}, {"id": 310037, "content": "毕业", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1474192}, {"id": 309782, "content": "经历不如意的事越多，越沉默，越成熟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497810}, {"id": 310038, "content": "智商", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498516}, {"id": 309783, "content": "不在轻易生气", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493101}, {"id": 310039, "content": "数学21题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498842}, {"id": 309784, "content": "熟练清理孩子排泄物以及更换尿不湿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496726}, {"id": 310040, "content": "看完一部演讲  感觉自己的三观被刷新了一次", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483612}, {"id": 309785, "content": "生病。每病一场，就对自己放松一点要求。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753653}, {"id": 309786, "content": "第一次性体验", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404922}, {"id": 310042, "content": "人生中一次又一次的离别，最后一次将会是和自己告别。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458046}]}